Company Overview
JAC Recruitment is an International Recruitment Agency, having its first business in the UK and expanding to other regions. As part of the TAZAKI Group, currently JAC Recruitment operates in 10 countries with 25 offices.JAC Recruitment Indonesia has been operating since 2002 and currently has 3 branches in Bekasi, Karawang, and Surabaya. Together with more than 100 consultants, we constantly aim to support each and every Client with the right people for the right position. And now, our Surabaya Office is grow fast along with Surabaya growth recently. We are expanding its business by add 2 additional Recruitment Consultant at Surabaya Office. We are welcome for any candidates who have strong mind, good interpersonal skill, and have a very deep service mind.
